Requirements
------------

- Python 2.3.4 or greater

- Zope 2.7.2 or greater

- CMF 1.4.3 or greater

- Plone 2.0.4 or greater

- Archetypes 1.3b3+

- libxml2 2.6.6+ (previous versions seem to have a bug validating RelaxNG)
